		<div id='newsContent'>
			<div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='https://www.ethz.ch/de/die-eth-zuerich/portraet/aktuelle-ehrungen-und-preise/2018/12/tech-oscar-fuer-professor-markus-gross-und-disney-research.html'>Tech Oscar</a>: <br/>Markus Gross and his co-inventors were awarded the Technical Achievement Award for their Medusa Performance Capture system.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='https://www.bilanz.ch/people/markus-gross-0'>Digital Shapers 2018</a>: <br/>Markus Gross was featured in the Digital Shapers 2018 by Bilanz magazine.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='https://graphics.ethz.ch/people/grossm/awards/awards.php'>Distinguished Career Award</a>: <br/>Markus Gross was awarded the Distinguished Career Award at Eurographics 2018.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='https://www.eurographics2018.nl'>Young Researcher Award</a>: <br/>Former CGL member Thabo Beeler received the Young Researcher Award at Eurographics 2018.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='https://graphics.ethz.ch/people/grossm/awards/awards.php'>Membership</a>: <br/>Markus Gross is now a member of the National Academy of Engineering of Korea.</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2018</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/publications/papers.php#Hol18a'>Award for Paper</a>: <br/>The paper &#8220;Parameter Space Comparison of Inertial Particle Models&#8221; by Holbein and G&uuml;nther won the <b>Best Paper Award</b> at VMV 2018</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/publications/papers.php#Ibr18b'>Award for Paper</a>: <br/>The paper &#8220;Visualization and Analysis of Deep Water Asteroid Impacts&#8221; by Imahorn, Baeza Rojo and G&uuml;nther won an <b>Honorable Mention Award</b> (1/2) at the IEEE Scientific Visualization Contest 2018</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2017</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='https://graphics.ethz.ch/people/grossm/awards/awards.php'>Membership</a>: <br/>Markus Gross is now a member of the Schweizerische Akademie der Technischen Wissenschaften (SATW).</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='https://www.ethz.ch/en/the-eth-zurich/education/awards/eth-medal.html'>Award for PhD thesis</a>: <br/>Recent CGL graduate Federico Perazzi was awarded an ETH medal for his outstanding Ph.D. thesis.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/publications/papers.php#Rim17a'>Award for Paper</a>: <br/>The paper &#8220;Visualization of Clouds and Atmospheric Air Flows&#8221; by Rimensberger, Gross and G&uuml;nther won the <b>IEEE Scientific Visualization Contest 2017</b> at IEEE VisWeek</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/publications/papers.php#Gun17d'>Award for Paper</a>: <br/>The paper &#8220;Visualization of Neural Network Predictions for Weather Forecasting&#8221; by Roesch and G&uuml;nther won an <b>Honorable Mention Award</b> (1/2) at VMV 2017</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/publications/papers.php#Kli17a'>Award for Paper</a>: <br/>The paper &#8220;Efficient Feature Embeddings for Student Classification with Variational Auto-encoders&#8221; by Klingler et al. won the <b>Best Paper Award</b> at EDM 2017</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/publications/papers.php#Mue17a'>Award for Paper</a>: <br/>The paper &#8220;Practical Path Guiding for Efficient Light-transport Simulation&#8221; by M&uuml;ller et al. won the <b>Best Paper Award</b> at EGSR 2017</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/publications/papers.php#Gun17b'>Award for Paper</a>: <br/>The paper &#8220;Flow-Induced Inertial Steady Vector Field Topology&#8221; by G&uuml;nther and Gross won an <b>Honorable Mention Award</b> (1/3) at Eurographics 2017</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://vcg.isti.cnr.it/cgf/winner.php'>Computer Graphics Forum 2017 Cover Image Contest</a>: <br/>The first two places of the CGF cover contest were obtained by CGL projects. M&uuml;ller et al. won first place, G&uuml;nther et al. won second place.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://www.forbes.com/profile/pascal-berard/'>Forbes 30 Under 30 Europe</a>: <br/>CGL Ph.D. student Pascal B�rard was chosen by Forbes as one of Europe�s most promising young game-changers.</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2016</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://www.heidelberg-laureate-forum.org/'>Heidelberg Laureate Forum 2016</a>: <br/>Dr. Cengiz �ztireli has been accepted to participate in the Heidelberg Laureate Forum 2016</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2015</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='https://www.ethz.ch/en/the-eth-zurich/education/awards/eth-medal.html'>Award for PhD thesis</a>: <br/>Recent CGL graduate Manuel Lang was awarded an ETH medal for his outstanding Ph.D. thesis.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://www.kutter-fonds.ethz.ch/PreviousPrizewinners.html'>Award for PhD thesis</a>: <br/>CGL researcher and Ph.D. graduate Tanja K�ser received the Fritz Kutter Award for her thesis.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://vgtc.org/sites/vgtc.org/attachments/awards/vis_career15.pdf'>Visualization Career Award</a>: <br/>Prof. Markus Gross has been awarded the Visualization Career Award.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/news/disney_small.png' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://www.disneyresearch.com/luciddreamsofgabriel'>&apos;Lucid Dreams of Gabriel&apos; presented at the Locarno film festival</a>: <br/>Experimental short film created by Disney Research Zurich in a collaboration with ETH and SRF showcasing the &apos;Flow of Time&apos; technique</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://www.fz-juelich.de/SharedDocs/Pressemitteilungen/UK/DE/2013/13-12-05beckurts-preis.html'>Karl Heinz Beckurts-Preis f�r Vorreiter der Computergrafik</a>: <br/>Prof. Markus Gross has been awarded the Karl Heinz Beckurts-Preis 2013</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://www.gi.de/wir-ueber-uns/personen/konrad-zuse-medaille/'>Konrad-Zuse-Medaille</a>: <br/>Prof. Markus Gross has been awarded the Konrad-Zuse-Medaille</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://www.ethz.ch/media/detail?pr_id=1140'>SciTech Oscar</a>: <br/>Prof. Markus Gross and former CGL postdoc win oscar for technical achievement</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2014</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='https://www.eg.org/index.php/awards/phd-award'>Best PhD Thesis Award</a>: <br/>Dr. Cengiz �ztireli has been awarded the Eurographics Annual Award for Best PhD Thesis 2014.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/publications/papers.php#Kae14b'>Award for Paper [Kae14b]</a>: <br/>The paper &#8220;Beyond Knowledge Tracing: Modeling Skill Topologies with Bayesian Networks&#8221; won the Best Paper Award at ITS 2014</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/hackathon'>AR Games Hackathon 2014</a>: <br/>Join the Augmented Reality Games Hackathon 2014!</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2012</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://www.acm.org/press-room/news-releases/2012/fellows-2012'>ACM Fellows</a>: <br/>Prof. Markus Gross recognized by ACM for outstanding contributions to computer graphics and animation</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/teaching/studentprojects'>Master Thesis Topics Available Now</a>: <br/>Please check our various new master thesis topics</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://www.bbaw.de/presse/pressemitteilungen/pressemitteilungen/neue-mitglieder-1'>Berlin-Brandenburg Academy of Sciences and Humanities</a>: <br/>Prof. Markus Gross becomes a member of BBAW</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/teaching/imsynth12'>New Course</a>: <br/><b>Image Synthesis</b> taught by Dr. Wojciech Jarosz from Disney Research Z�rich</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2011</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/publications/papers.php#Sol11b'>Award for Paper [Sol11b]</a>: <br/>The paper &#8220;SPH Based Shallow Water Simulation&#8221; won the <b>Best Paper Award</b> at VRIPhys 2011</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://www.inf.ethz.ch/news/spotlight/Swiss_ICT'>Swiss ICT Award</a>: <br/>Prof. Markus Gross honored with the Swiss ICT Award 2011</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2010</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/news/disney_small.png' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://zurich.disneyresearch.com/'>Disney Research Zurich</a>: <br/>Disney Research Laboratory at ETH Zurich officially openend in April. Prof. Markus Gross is the director.</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2009</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/teaching/gamelab09'>GameLab Presentations</a>: <br/>Public presentation of Game Programming Laboratory projects, Thursday, May 28</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/~malang/survey/'>Video Retargeting Survey</a>: <br/>Please take part in this user study on video rescaling!</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/publications/papers.php#Ozt09'>Award for Paper [Ozt09]</a>: <br/>Cengiz &Ouml;ztireli won the <b>Best Student Paper Award</b> at Eurographics 2009.</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2008</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/news/disney_small.png' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://zurich.disneyresearch.com/'>Disney Research Zurich</a>: <br/>Disney launches new Research Laboratory at ETH Zurich. Prof. Markus Gross is the director.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/publications/papers.php#Mar08'>Award for Paper [Mar08]</a>: <br/>Sebastian Martin won the <b>Best Student Paper Award</b> at SGP 2008.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/publications/papers.php#Hein08b'>Award for Paper [Hein08b]</a>: <br/>Simon Heinzle won the <b>Best Paper Award</b> at Graphics Hardware 2008.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/dybuster'>Dybuster Dyslexia Study</a>: <br/>A user study to evaluate our new software for dyslexia therapy.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/teaching/masterprogram.php'>Master - Visual Computing</a>: <br/>Check our major program in Visual Computing</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/teaching/gamelab08'>New Course</a>: <br/>Game Programming Laboratory SS08</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2007</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://www.dybuster.ch'>New Spin-off: Dybuster AG</a>: <br/>Dybuster focuses on the development of scientifically based and computer-assisted therapy for individuals with learning difficulties and neurobiological disabilities.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://www.liberovision.com'>New Spin-off: LiberoVision</a>: <br/>LiberoVision provides a ground-breaking technology to view controversial or tactically interesting football/soccer scenes from arbitrary viewpoints.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://www.eg.org/about/awards/winners/winner_botsch'>Young Researcher Award</a>: <br/>Mario Botsch received the Young Researcher Award of the Eurographics Association.</div></div><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/publications/papers.php#Zie07c'>Award for Paper [Zie07c]</a>: <br/>Remo Ziegler won the Best Paper Award of Eurographics 2007.</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2006</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newstrophy.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/publications/papers.php#Bot06a'>Award for Paper [Bot06a]</a>: <br/>Mario Botsch won the Best Paper Award at the EG Symposium on Geometry Processing 2006.</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2004</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/pointshop3d/'>Pointshop 3D</a>: <br/>Version 2.0 now available.</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2002</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href=''>New Spin-off: NovodeX</a>: <br/>NovodeX provides a physics engine middleware for computer games.</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>2000</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href=''>New Spin-off: Cyfex AG</a>: <br/>Cyfex helps physical modeling for facial surgery simulation.</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>1997</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/'>Full Professor</a>: <br/>Markus Gross becomes Full Professor.</div></div><h3 class='newsarchive'>1994</h3><div class='item'><div class='image'><img src='http://graphics.ethz.ch/images/newscgl.gif' alt='' /></div><div class='text'><a href='http://graphics.ethz.ch/'>Foundation of CGL</a>: <br/>Markus Gross becomes Assistant Professor at ETH and founds the Computer Graphics Laboratory.</div></div>		</div>
